data.comment: The match has started.

Free kick Eibar.

In Eibar, Sergi Enrich (Eibar) gets his head to the ball but the strike is cleared by an untiring defence.
Pablo Gonzales Fuertes signals a free kick to Eibar in their own half.
Levante push forward at Ipurua Municipal Stadium and Borja Mayoral gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Eibar defence.
